title: Why Does Nobody Speak Truth About The Prusa I3 Mk.3? - It's Overhyped and Over Priced.

media:group.media:title: Why Does Nobody Speak Truth About The Prusa I3 Mk.3? - It's Overhyped and Over Priced.
media:group.media:description:
Prusa Fanboys all seem to suffer from the Sunk Cost Fallacy: https://time.com/5347133/sunk-cost-fallacy-decisions/#:~:text=%E2%80%9CThe%20sunk%20cost%20effect%20is,the%20author%20of%20a%202018
This channel has a long history of criticizing Prusa and because nobody else is willing to say these things (for fear of the toxic Prusa mob) Design Prototype Test has become a punching bag in many 3D printer forums across the internet. I have been branded as an unreasonable hater of Prusa. Let's see what happens when I actually get my hands on a Prusa I3 Mk.3.
